24:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white pt-16 pb-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]","children":[["$","article",null,{"data-progress-target":true,"className":"max-w-3xl prose-base","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"We run CRO programmes for both US and UK clients, and after a few years the pattern is clear: British audiences respond to a different rhetorical register. American playbooks lifted wholesale tend to underperform here. These are eight A/B tests we've shipped for UK clients that significantly outperformed control — and the cultural reasons we think they worked."}],["$","h2","1",{"id":"test-1-price","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#test-1-price","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Test 1: Show the actual price, not 'Get a Quote'"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"A B2B fintech client had 'Request a Quote' across the pricing page. We A/B tested it against 'From £X/month' with a tooltip explaining what affects the final price. Trial signups up 31%. British buyers are price-skeptical and read 'Request a Quote' as 'we're about to upcharge you'."}],["$","h2","3",{"id":"test-2-testimonials","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#test-2-testimonials","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Test 2: Named UK testimonials beat generic 'industry leaders'"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Replacing 'trusted by industry leaders' (with logos) with three named testimonials from recognisable UK companies (with full names, roles, and a small headshot) lifted trial conversion by 18%. British buyers find logo walls suspicious — they want to see a real person at a real UK company who used the product."}],["$","h2","5",{"id":"test-3-cta","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#test-3-cta","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Test 3: 'Book a call' beat 'Get started' on B2B services"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"On a UK consultancy site, 'Get started' as the primary CTA underperformed 'Book a call' by 22%. The vocabulary of 'getting started' is American-coded. British B2B buyers expect to talk to a human before they commit."}],["$","h2","7",{"id":"test-4-urgency","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#test-4-urgency","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Test 4: Remove false urgency"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"'Limited spots available' and '24-hour offer' banners reduced conversion on three different UK B2B tests we ran. British audiences read these as a sales gimmick and disengage. We replaced them with a quiet reassurance message — 'Trusted by 240 UK businesses since 2019' — and conversion rose."}],"$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31"],"$undefined","$L32","$L33","$L34"]}],"$L35"]}]}]
